## Streaming Context Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Pipeline as ParallelContextPipeline
    participant Cache as ContextCache
    participant DB as Prisma
    participant Embed as EmbeddingService

    Client->>Pipeline: assembleStreaming(params)
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yield 1: Identity Core (Priority 100)
    Pipeline->>Cache: getBundle(userId, 'identity_core')
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Pipeline: cached bundle
    else Cache Miss
        Pipeline->>DB: find contextBundle
        DB-->>Pipeline: bundle
        Pipeline->>Cache: setBundle
    end
    Pipeline-->>Client: {layer: 'identity_core', priority: 100}
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yield 2: Global Preferences (Priority 90)
    Pipeline->>Cache: getBundle(userId, 'global_prefs')
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Pipeline: cached bundle
    else Cache Miss
        Pipeline->>DB: find contextBundle
        DB-->>Pipeline: bundle
    end
    Pipeline-->>Client: {layer: 'global_prefs', priority: 90}
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yield 3-5: Topics (Priority 70)
    Pipeline->>Embed: embedMessage(userMessage)
    Embed-->>Pipeline: embedding
    Pipeline->>DB: semantic search topic_profiles
    DB-->>Pipeline: topic matches
    loop for each topic
        Pipeline->>Cache: getBundle(userId, 'topic', profileId)
        Pipeline-->>Client: {layer: 'topic:slug', priority: 70}
    end
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yield 6-8: Entities (Priority 60)
    Pipeline->>DB: semantic search entity_profiles
    DB-->>Pipeline: entity matches
    loop for each entity
        Pipeline->>Cache: getBundle(userId, 'entity', entityId)
        Pipeline-->>Client: {layer: 'entity:name', priority: 60}
    end
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yield 9: Conversation (Priority 80)
    alt conversationId provided
        Pipeline->>Cache: getBundle(userId, 'conversation', convId)
        Pipeline-->>Client: {layer: 'conversation', priority: 80}
    end
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yield 10: JIT Knowledge (Priority 50)
    Pipeline->>DB: semantic search atomic_chat_units
    Pipeline->>DB: semantic search memories
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: formatJITContent
    Pipeline-->>Client: {layer: 'jit_knowledge', priority: 50, isFinal: true}
```

